  "summary": "OpenStack Identity Keystone Privilege Escalation vulnerability",
  "details": "The LDAP backend in OpenStack Identity (Keystone) Grizzly and Havana, when removing a role on a tenant for a user who does not have that role, adds the role to the user, which allows local users to gain privileges.",
